A video showing two military vehicles as well as a vehicle from the South African Military Health Service allegedly patrolling the streets of Westenburg. The source who supplied the video alleged that the vehicles were seen in one of the streets in the neighbourhood. The person filming the vehicles can also be heard thanking the military for keeping people living in isolation safe.

